msgctxt "84_Shifty-eyed Man"
msgid "Excuse me. Are you looking for something?"
msgstr "Excuse me. Are you looking for something?"

msgctxt "96_Tanimura"
msgid "...You know a place called the Dragon Palace? I heard it was around here somewhere."
msgstr "...You know a place called the Dragon Palace? I heard it was around here somewhere."

msgctxt "108_Shifty-eyed Man"
msgid "Dragon Palace, huh? I may know something... But it's not\\r\n"\n"the kind of place that just anybody can get into."
msgstr "Dragon Palace, huh? I may know something... But it's not\\r\n"\n"the kind of place that just anybody can get into."

msgctxt "120_Tanimura"
msgid "Any details you can give?"
msgstr "Any details you can give?"

msgctxt "132_Shifty-eyed Man"
msgid "You know the building under construction on this street?\\r\n"\n"It's in the building next to that."
msgstr "You know the building under construction on this street?\\r\n"\n"It's in the building next to that."

msgctxt "144_Tanimura"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr "Gracias."

